'''Andrew Hessel''' is a micro-biologist and geneticist and entrepreur. He founded the Pink Army Cooperative, and Humane Genomics, Inc.<ref>[http://andrewhessel.com/ Andrew Hessel bio from his own website]</ref><ref>[http://www.bioinnovate.co/andrew-hessel.html Andrew Hessel bio at bioinnovate.co]</ref> Between 2012-2017, he was a Distinguished Researcher at [[Autodesk| Autodesk Life Sciences]].<ref>[https://www.autodeskresearch.com/people/andrew-hessel Andrew Hessel bio at AutoDesk Research]</ref><ref>[https://medium.com/neodotlife/andrew-hessel-human-genome-project-write-d15580dd0885 The Human Operating System Gets an Overhaul]</ref> Hessel is co-chair of Bioinformatics and Biotechnology at [[Singularity University]], and a fellow at the Institute for Science, Society, and Policy at the [[University of Ottawa]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://su.org/about/faculty/andrew-hessel/|title=Faculty - Andrew Hessel|publisher=Singularity University}}</ref> He is also involved in Genome Project-Write.{{citation needed|date=May 2018}}

