This is a list of notable [[self-immolation]]s done for political reasons. Non-political self-immolations are not included in the list. Self-immolation has become an increasingly used protest tactic among [[Tibet]]ans protesting rule of Tibet by China<ref>Sharon LaFraniere, [https://www.nytimes.com/2012/01/10/world/asia/3-monks-deaths-show-rise-of-self-immolation-among-tibetans.html More Monks Die by Fire in Protest of Beijing], ''[[New York Times]]'', January 9, 2012</ref> and [[Arabs]] against various Arab governments.<ref>Nada Bakri, [https://www.nytimes.com/2012/01/21/world/africa/self-immolation-on-the-rise-in-the-arab-world.html Self-Immolation Is on the Rise in the Arab World], ''New York Times'', January 20, 2012.</ref>

